In [3]:
def Logistic(ts,cap,floor,fourier_order):
    ts.index = pd.date_range('2001','2020',freq='Q-DEC')
    ts = ts.dropna(axis=0,how='any')
    ts = ts.reset_index()
    ts.columns=['ds','y']
    ts['cap'] = cap
    ts['floor'] = floor
    ts.head()
    model = Prophet(growth='logistic',weekly_seasonality=False,daily_seasonality=False,yearly_seasonality=False,changepoint_range=1,
                    changepoint_prior_scale=0.5,interval_width=0.6,seasonality_mode='multiplicative')
    model.add_seasonality(name='monthly', period=30.5, fourier_order=fourier_order)
    model.fit(ts)
    future = model.make_future_dataframe(periods = 4, freq = 'Q-DEC')  
    future['cap'] = cap
    future['floor'] = floor
    forecast = model.predict(future)
    result = forecast[['ds', 'yhat', 'yhat_lower', 'yhat_upper']].tail(4)
    return model,forecast,result

def Linear(ts,fourier_order):
    ts.index = pd.date_range('2001','2020',freq='Q-DEC')
    ts = ts.dropna(axis=0,how='any')
    ts = ts.reset_index()
    ts.columns=['ds','y']
    model = Prophet(growth='linear',weekly_seasonality=False,daily_seasonality=False,yearly_seasonality=False,changepoint_range=1,
                changepoint_prior_scale=0.5,interval_width=0.6)
    model.add_seasonality(name='monthly', period=30.5,fourier_order=fourier_order)
    model.fit(ts)
    future = model.make_future_dataframe(periods = 4, freq = 'Q-DEC')  
    forecast = model.predict(future)
    result = forecast[['ds', 'yhat', 'yhat_lower', 'yhat_upper']].tail(4)
    return model,forecast,result

sum_na1 = pd.merge(G2_NA_2020.iloc[:,0:2], G3_NA_2020.iloc[:,0:2], how='inner',on='ds',
                  suffixes=('_2G', '_3G'), copy=True, indicator=False)
sum_na2 = pd.merge(G4_NA_2020.iloc[:,0:2], G5_NA_2020.iloc[:,0:2], how='inner',on='ds',
                  suffixes=('_4G', '_5G'), copy=True, indicator=False)
sum_na = pd.merge(sum_na1, sum_na2, how='inner',on='ds')
sum_na.set_index('ds',inplace=True)
sum_na['sum'] = sum_na.apply(lambda x: x.sum(), axis=1)
sum_na.to_excel('sum_na.xlsx')
